{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And before I went there, I went to my cousin-- to that cousin, Naftali Backenroth, and-- to say goodbye to him, to thank him for what he did for me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And sure enough, there was another friend of ours, a Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Liever. ?] He's still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He lives in Queens, New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He said, let me just take a look at your pockets, what you have in your pockets before you leave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Sure enough, he found in the-- in the pocket a family picture of my grandfather with a beard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he took it away from me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He says, if they find that picture with you or on you, you're-- you're-- you're dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I remembered-- I remembered that since this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we started walking to Lishnya.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I took off the band.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was nervous, because I was so-- so accustomed to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was nervous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we just passed the boundaries of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The Ukrainian police stopped us, because there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I believe 10 o'clock at night, you couldn't-- nobody was supposed to leave the-- leave the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he stopped us, because it was past 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he's leading us to so-called gendarmerie, the German-- German Schutzpolizei.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Here, I felt, here's the end of my career.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I just left house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and I'm going to Lishnya.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they've caught me already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They brought us to the police station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I looked at this brother of the Voloshyn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He was white like a-- like a sheet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He lost his speech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he couldn't talk, because he had a lot to lose.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I had nothing to lose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "He had a lot to lose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He was stiff.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
